# ==========================================
# Rust / Cargo Output
# ==========================================
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

# Note: Keep Cargo.lock if this is an end-user application binary,
# but ignore it if it's strictly a library/wheel build. For a desktop app,
# keeping it tracked is standard, but you can uncomment the line above if needed.

